"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.1.8.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.1.8.1</span> 標題：禾場（threshing floor）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Aramaic</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">蘭：אִדְּרֵי</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’idar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:35\">DAN 2:35</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： גֹּרֶן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： goren)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:20\">NUM 15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:27\">NUM 18:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:30\">NUM 18:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:14\">DEU 15:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:13\">DEU 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:37\">JDG 6:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:2\">RUT 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:3\">RUT 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:6\">RUT 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:14\">RUT 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:1\">1SA 23:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:16\">2SA 24:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:18\">2SA 24:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:21\">2SA 24:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:24\">2SA 24:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:10\">1KI 22:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:27\">2KI 6:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:15\">1CH 21:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:18\">1CH 21:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:21\">1CH 21:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:22\">1CH 21:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:28\">1CH 21:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:1\">2CH 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:9\">2CH 18:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:12\">JOB 39:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:10\">ISA 21:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:25\">JER 2:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:33\">JER 51:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:1\">HOS 9:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:2\">HOS 9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:3\">HOS 13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:24\">JOL 2:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:12\">MIC 4:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἅλων</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： halōn)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:12\">MAT 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:17\">LUK 3:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Latin</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">拉： area</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd4:30\">2ES 4:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd4:39\">2ES 4:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd9:17\">2ES 9:17</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0322_threshing_floor.jpg\" alt=\"打穀場\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">打穀場 (© Klearchos Kapoutsis, CC BY 2.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>禾場是一塊平坦的圓形區域，直徑約7.5—12米（25—40英呎），通常位於種植穀物的田地附近，並且盡量選在有風吹過的高處（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.1.8.3 揚場木杈 (winnowing fork)&lt;REALIA:1.1.8.3&gt;</a> ）。禾場通常位於村莊附近，以便保護穀物。禾場可以是基岩，也可以是夯實的泥地。禾場的邊緣常會圍上石塊，將穀物圍在其中。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>割下麥子之後，還需要將子粒與麥稈和外殼分離。割下的麥子擺放在禾場上。麥稈和外殼與子粒分離的方法有以下幾種：（1）將脫粒板從麥子上方拖過去（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.1.8.2 打穀機、脫粒板 (threshing board, sledge)&lt;REALIA:1.1.8.2&gt;</a> ）；（2）讓牲畜在麥子上面來回踩踏；（3）用工具敲打。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:33\">JER 51:33</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:12\">MIC 4:12</a> ，用於踹穀的禾場象徵著審判或刑罰。如果人們不知道穀物脫粒的過程，或者不明白穀物脫粒是什麼意思，那麼翻譯者可以明白表述；例如，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:12\">MIC 4:12</a> b可以譯成，「他們沒有意識到他們已被聚集在一起受懲罰，就像穀物被運到禾場脫粒那樣」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直譯）。另外，比較《〈馬太福音〉手冊》（<em>A Handbook on The Gospel of Matthew</em> ，第70頁）關於<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:12\">MAT 3:12</a> 的另一種建議譯法：「他預備好進行審判，將好人與壞人分開，就像農夫準備用簸箕將麥子與麥糠分開；他將保證好人的安全，就像農夫將麥子放入糧倉；他必將惡人扔在永不止息的火中焚燒，就像農夫清除禾場上的糠秕，將其燒掉一樣。」</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:12\">MAT 3:12</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:17\">LUK 3:17</a> ，<em>halōn</em> 一詞表示「禾場」的意思進行了引申，這裡是指仍然留在禾場上面的、已脫粒的穀物。如果將這裡原文字面意為「要揚淨他的禾場」一語譯為「他要徹底揚淨所有的穀物」，那麼經文的意思就會十分清楚。另一方面，翻譯者也可以字面解釋這兩處新約經文中<em>halōn</em> 的意思，譯為「他要揚淨他的禾場」，意即聚攏穀物並去除麥稈和麥糠。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
